  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in an elevated position at the top of the nursery slopes, with panoramic views of the mountains and village, this well appointed four star hotel offers a 2,000m² leisure area including a heated outdoor pool and a cosy hut where guests can enjoy a free daily lunch snack. An excellent selection of wines is available in the popular wine cellar and local farm produce is used for meals. The hotel is especially suitable for families with free child supervision on offer and its location close to the ski school meeting place.</p>]]></description>
